### 健康检查
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/

### 显式新建空会话
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/conversations

### 新建会话并流式聊天
# 运行前请先在 .env 中配置 ANTHROPIC_API_KEY、ANTHROPIC_MODEL，必要时可额外配置 ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL
# thinking_enabled=true 会进入主聊天流，并返回 chunk + 链式 trace_step/trace_done
# 请从首个 conversation 事件里记录 run_id，供“终止当前生成”接口使用
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation_id": "{{conversation_id}}",
  "message": "查一下 207.97.137.107",
  "thinking_enabled": true
}

### Planner 路由模式：首次发消息时隐式创建会话
# thinking_enabled=false 会先做路由，再继续回复
# 如果命中 simple，只返回 chunk；如果命中 complex/agent，才会返回 route/planner_done + trace_step
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "你好",
  "thinking_enabled": false
}

### Planner 命中复杂路径
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "帮我查一下这个 IP 的归属和来源",
  "thinking_enabled": false
}

### 终止当前生成
# 将 {{run_id}} 替换成当前 SSE 首个 conversation 事件返回的 run_id
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/runs/{{run_id}}/stop

### 查询会话列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/conversations

### 查询单个会话详情
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/conversations/{{conversation_id}}

### 更新会话标题
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/conversations/{{conversation_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "短期记忆设计讨论"
}

### 删除会话
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/conversations/{{conversation_id}}

@anthropic_base_url = https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic
@planner_model = MiniMax-M2
@planner_user_message = 帮我查一下这个 IP 的归属和来源
@run_id = 6e0f1938-897a-4dda-b17c-1c33d7ef8d24

### 直连上游模型：复现 planner 请求
# 目的：验证 route/plan/tools 的原始模型输出，而不是经过服务端 SSE 包装后的结果
# 运行前请在 HTTP Client 环境中提供 anthropic_api_key 变量，或手动替换下面请求头
POST {{anthropic_base_url}}/v1/messages
x-api-key: {{anthropic_api_key}}
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{planner_model}}",
  "max_tokens": 256,
  "thinking": {
    "type": "disabled"
  },
  "system": "You are the reasoning and execution planner for an AI chat system. Your job is NOT to answer the user directly. Classify the request into one of: simple, complex, agent. If route is simple, return exactly {\"route\":\"simple\"}. If route is complex, return exactly {\"route\":\"complex\",\"plan\":[...]}. If route is agent, return exactly {\"route\":\"agent\",\"plan\":[...],\"tools\":[...]}. Allowed tools: web_search, http_fetch. Always return valid JSON only. Do not wrap JSON in markdown. Do not include any explanation or extra keys.",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "{{planner_user_message}}"
    }
  ]
}
